---
import IconLink from "../components/IconLink.astro";
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";

---



<Layout>
	
	<header  class="grid grid-cols-4 px-5  pt-0 pb-5 gap-y-1   border gradiente-1  ">
	
	<div class="w-40 tra rounded-full col-span-6 sm:col-span-1 mx-auto sm:mx-0 my-5   overflow-hidden transition ease-in duration-700  " >
		<img class="object-cover" src="/void1499/images/me.jpeg" alt="">
	</div>
	
	<p class="font-medium col-span-6 " >
		Tecnico en programacion y analisis de sistemas 
	</p>
	
	<h1 data-animation="slide-right" class="font-semibold text-2xl sm:text-3xl col-span-5   text-start ">
		Desarrollo web Frontend/Backend.Diseño UI. <br>
	</h1>
	
	<h2 class="text-medium  col-span-5 " >
		erick.olivares.gonzalez@gmail.com
	</h2>
	<div class="col-span-1 row-span-2 flex flex-col gap-y-5  col-start-6 row-start-3 " >
			<IconLink  class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/linkedin.svg" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/erick-olivares/"  ></IconLink>
			<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" href="https://github.com/VOID1499" ></IconLink>
	</div>
	
	
	
	</header>


		

	<section  class="w-full flex flex-col xl:flex-row px-10 sm:px-0    gap-5 sm:gap-2 " >

		<div data-animation="slide-up"  class="w-full xl:w-1/3  rounded-sm border border-gray-600 rounded-sm filter drop-shadow-lg py-5  delay-0  opacity-0" >
			<ul class="w-full flex flex-wrap justify-center  gap-2 " >
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/javascript.svg" alt="Javascript" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/typescript.svg" alt="Typescript" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/angular.svg" alt="Angular" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/rxjs.svg" alt="RxJs" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/tailwind.svg" alt="tailwind" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/html.svg" alt="html" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/css.svg" alt="css" ></IconLink>
			</ul>
			<h1 class="text-center mt-5" >Frontend</h1>
		</div>

		<div data-animation="slide-up" class="w-full xl:w-1/3  rounded-sm border border-gray-600 rounded-sm filter drop-shadow-lg py-5  delay-1  opacity-0 " >
			<ul class="w-full flex flex flex-wrap justify-center  gap-2 " >
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/node.svg" alt="NodeJs" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/dotnet.svg" alt=".NET" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/c-sharp.svg" alt="C-sharp" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/mysql.svg" alt="MySql" ></IconLink>
			</ul>
			<h1 class="text-center mt-5" >Backend</h1>
		</div>

		<div data-animation="slide-up" class="w-full xl:w-1/3  rounded-sm border border-gray-600 rounded-sm filter drop-shadow-lg py-5  delay-2  opacity-0" >
			<ul class="w-full flex flex flex-wrap justify-center  gap-2 " >
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/git.svg" alt="Git" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" alt="Github" ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-7" src="/void1499/icons/figma.svg" alt="Figma" ></IconLink>
			</ul>
			<h1 class="text-center mt-5" >Otras herramientas</h1>
		</div>
	

	</section>



	<article data-animation="slide-left"  class="h-auto flex flex-col rounded-sm mx-10 sm:mx-0  flex-wrap gap-3 border gradiente-1  opacity-0">
		
		<div class="w-full h-auto flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-5  py-5 px-5 sm:px-10 " >
			<h1 class="text-semibold text-2xl " >Cliente Unsplash API</h1>
			<p class="w-auto  text-left ">
				Cliente de la <span class="font-semibold text-green-300" >APIR REST</span> de <a
				class="underline font-semibold text-green-300" target="_blank" href="https://unsplash.com/es">Unsplash</a>
				que proporciona imágenes con calidad profesional de todo el mundo.
				Frontend hecho con <span class="text-green-300 font-semibold" >Angular</span> v.17. y <span class="text-green-300 font-semibold" >Tailwind CSS</span>
			</p>

			<span class="w-auto ml-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 ">
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" href="https://github.com/VOID1499/unsplashapi"  ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" href="https://github.com/VOID1499/unsplashapi"  ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/external-link.svg" href="https://void1499.github.io/unsplashapi"  ></IconLink>
			</span>
			
		</div>

	</article>

	<article data-animation="slide-right" class="h-auto flex flex-col rounded-sm mx-10 sm:mx-0  flex-wrap gap-3 border gradiente-1  opacity-0">
		
		<div class="w-full h-auto flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-5  py-5 px-5 sm:px-10 " >
			<h1 class="text-semibold text-2xl " >Task App</h1>
			<p class="w-auto  text-left ">
				Una app basica de tareas con respaldo de datos como usuario y tareas en el lado del backend.
				Despliegue del servidor con <span class="font-semibold text-green-300" >NodeJs</span> y  <span class="font-semibold text-green-300" >Express</span> en la plataforma de <a target="_blank" href="https://render.com/" class="underline font-semibold text-green-300" >Render</a> asi como tambien el sitio estatico hecho con <span class="text-green-300 font-semibold" >Angular</span> y <span class="text-green-300 font-semibold" >Bootstrap</span>  en sus versiones modulares.
				Los datos se encuentran alojados en la plataforma de <a
				class="underline font-semibold text-green-300" target="_blank" href="https://www.mongodb.com/es/cloud/atlas">MongoDB Atlas</a>.


			</p>

			<span class="w-auto ml-auto flex flex-wrap gap-2 ">
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" href="https://github.com/VOID1499/node-express-01"  ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/github.svg" href="https://github.com/VOID1499/taskAPP"  ></IconLink>
				<IconLink class="w-6" src="/void1499/icons/external-link.svg" href="https://task-app-rtam.onrender.com/"  ></IconLink>
			</span>
			
		</div>

	</article>


	

	


	
</Layout>